    function oninitframework()
    {
      nexacro._initHTMLSysEvent(window, document);
      nexacro._prepareManagerFrame();

      /* 2022.03.17 cyb2000k 정보서비스 모바일모드 관련 ----------------------------------------- */
      var frmUrl = location.href;
      var varCut = frmUrl.indexOf("?");
      var varCheck = frmUrl.substring(varCut+1);
      var varList = varCheck.split("&");
      application._globalvalue = varList;
      /* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- */

      application.load("infoservice", "infoservice.xadl.js");
    }
    function onfinalframework()
    {
      
    }
  </script>

    <script type="text/javascript">
    function dialog() {

        var dialogBox = $('.dialog'),
        dialogTrigger = $('.dialog__trigger'),
        dialogClose = $('.dialog__close'),
        dialogTitle = $('.dialog__title'),
        dialogContent = $('.dialog__content'),
        dialogAction = $('.dialog__action');

        // Open the dialog
        dialogTrigger.on('click', function(e) {
            dialogBox.toggleClass('dialog--active');
            e.stopPropagation()
        });

        // Close the dialog - click close button
        dialogClose.on('touchstart click', function() {
            dialogBox.removeClass('dialog--active');
            dialogBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
        });

        // Close the dialog - press escape key // key#27
        $(document).keyup(function(e) {
            if (e.keyCode === 27) {
                dialogBox.removeClass('dialog--active');
                dialogBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
            }
        });

        // Close dialog - click outside
        dialogBox.on("touchstart click", function(e) {
            if ($(e.target).is(dialogBox) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogTitle) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogContent) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogAction) === false) {
                  dialogBox.removeClass("dialog--active");
                  dialogBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
            }
        });
  
        dialogBox.toggleClass('dialog--active');
    };

    function dialogNotice() {
        //console.log("펑션");
        var dialogNoticeBox = $('.dialogNotice'),
        dialogNoticeTrigger = $('.dialogNotice__trigger'),
        dialogNoticeClose = $('.dialogNotice__close'),
        dialogNoticeTitle = $('.dialogNotice__title'),
        dialogNoticeContent = $('.dialogNotice__content'),
        dialogNoticeAction = $('.dialogNotice__action');
        
        //console.log(dialogNoticeBox);

        // Open the dialog
        dialogNoticeTrigger.on('click', function(e) {
            //console.log("오픈");
            dialogNoticeBox.toggleClass('dialogNotice--active');
            e.stopPropagation()
        });

        // Close the dialog - click close button
        dialogNoticeClose.on('touchstart click', function() {
            dialogNoticeBox.removeClass('dialogNotice--active');
            dialogNoticeBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
        });

        // Close the dialog - press escape key // key#27
        $(document).keyup(function(e) {
            if (e.keyCode === 27) {
                dialogNoticeBox.removeClass('dialogNotice--active');
                dialogNoticeBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
            }
        });

        // Close dialog - click outside
        dialogNoticeBox.on("touchstart click", function(e) {
            //console.log("터치");
            if ($(e.target).is(dialogNoticeBox) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogNoticeTitle) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogNoticeContent) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogNoticeAction) === false) {
                   //console.log("이벤트");
                  dialogNoticeBox.removeClass("dialogNotice--active");
                  dialogNoticeBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
            }
        });
        dialogNoticeBox.toggleClass('dialogNotice--active');
    };
    function dialogGate() {
        //console.log("펑션");
        var dialogGateBox = $('.dialogGate'),
        dialogGateTrigger = $('.dialogGate__trigger'),
        dialogGateClose = $('.dialogGate__close'),
        dialogGateTitle = $('.dialogGate__title'),
        dialogGateContent = $('.dialogGate__content'),
        dialogGateAction = $('.dialogGate__action');
        
        //console.log(dialogNoticeBox);

        // Open the dialog
        dialogGateTrigger.on('click', function(e) {
            //console.log("오픈");
            dialogGateBox.toggleClass('dialogGate--active');
            e.stopPropagation()
        });

        // Close the dialog - click close button
        dialogGateClose.on('touchstart click', function() {
            dialogGateBox.removeClass('dialogGate--active');
            dialogGateBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
        });

        // Close the dialog - press escape key // key#27
        $(document).keyup(function(e) {
            if (e.keyCode === 27) {
                dialogGateBox.removeClass('dialogGate--active');
                dialogGateBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
            }
        });

        // Close dialog - click outside
        dialogGateBox.on("touchstart click", function(e) {
            //console.log("터치");
            if ($(e.target).is(dialogGateBox) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogGateTitle) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogGateContent) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogGateAction) === false) {
                   //console.log("이벤트");
                  dialogGateBox.removeClass("dialogGate--active");
                  dialogGateBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
            }
        });
        dialogGateBox.toggleClass('dialogGate--active');
    };
    function dialogLimit() {
        //console.log("펑션");
        var dialogLimitBox = $('.dialogLimit'),
        dialogLimitTrigger = $('.dialogLimit__trigger'),
        dialogLimitClose = $('.dialogLimit__close'),
        dialogLimitTitle = $('.dialogLimit__title'),
        dialogLimitContent = $('.dialogLimit__content'),
        dialogLimitAction = $('.dialogLimit__action');
        
        //console.log(dialogNoticeBox);

        // Open the dialog
        dialogLimitTrigger.on('click', function(e) {
            //console.log("오픈");
            dialogLimitBox.toggleClass('dialogLimit--active');
            e.stopPropagation()
        });

        // Close the dialog - click close button
        dialogLimitClose.on('touchstart click', function() {
            dialogLimitBox.removeClass('dialogLimit--active');
            dialogLimitBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
        });

        // Close the dialog - press escape key // key#27
        $(document).keyup(function(e) {
            if (e.keyCode === 27) {
                dialogLimitBox.removeClass('dialogLimit--active');
                dialogLimitBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
            }
        });

        // Close dialog - click outside
        dialogLimitBox.on("touchstart click", function(e) {
            //console.log("터치");
            if ($(e.target).is(dialogLimitBox) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogLimitTitle) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogLimitContent) === false &&
                      $(e.target).is(dialogLimitAction) === false) {
                   //console.log("이벤트");
                  dialogLimitBox.removeClass("dialogLimit--active");
                  dialogLimitBox.css({"width":"0", "height":"0", "top":"500px"});
            }
        });
        dialogLimitBox.toggleClass('dialogLimit--active');
    };
    // Run function when the document has loaded
    $(function() {
          dialog();
          dialogNotice();
          dialogGate();
          dialogLimit();
    });

	function mainTabClose()
	{
		var objRemoveTabName = application.uarguments["workframe"].frames[0].name;
		application.uarguments['tabframe'].form.fn_deleteTab( objRemoveTabName );
	}
    </script>
